thread.title: Unhappy

author: Unhappy
title: Unhappy
text: I received 2 boxes of lenses one was colored light blue and labeled made in the USA, the other was labeled made in Ireland with a dark blue color scheme. I was concerned about why the packages were different and they were from different countries so I email them to inquire and never heard back. The box from Ireland was also discolored with yellowing on the bar code. This made me suspicious, I won't order from them again.
